                    <span>I have both the 1st edition and 2nd editions. It is the most logical and complete valuation text around. Takes you through valuation processes as well as compares various methods step-by-step, logically and rationally. I also have the McKinsey edition and although it's good, it cannot compare with Damodaran's in clarity of language and logical reasoning.</span>
                  
              
